<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Newsletter</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Displays if the contact receives the newsletter. It is not possible to activate this option manually. In order to exclude the contact from receiving the newsletter, click on <strong>Delete newsletter</strong>.</p></td>
