<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Blocked</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select whether or not the contact should be blocked for the specific client.<br>
If the option is activated, the contact is blocked and can no longer log into the online store. If the option is deactivated, the contact is able to log into the online store.</p></td>
