<div class="paragraph">
<p>Each data record contains the history of a contact. The history includes e.g. how long the contact has been registered and when he or she has been logged into your online store for the last time and when the last order was generated. This data is automatically updated and cannot be changed.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Displaying the history:</p>
</div>
