<h3 id="4300">17.3. Searching for a property</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Properties are centrally managed in the <strong>System » Settings » Properties</strong> menu. After opening the menu, start the search to display the properties. In order to search for specific properties, enter a search term in the search fields. The drop-down lists help you search for properties that share specific criteria. You can combine as many search filters as you like.</p>
</div>
